ygData.messageBody:
I gotta say that all questions about where to hunt, how to do things, what
equip etc. can all be found in one wonderful location: www.eqdiva.com

That site has helped me get to (just shy of) 52 in a little over 5 months
of only part-time playing. There is SO much information there, the forums
have so many knowledgeable people, its really amazing. You should check it
out.

Cresh Enddo
Siren of 51 songs
Legion of Valor
Bristlebane
